                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-17a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-01T23:24:15.198+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="KR3a0014-en">that means there will be no music in All Under Heaven;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-17a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-01T23:24:18.719+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="KR3a0014-zh-287cbdf3">天下就没有乐教了；只谈虚文而不谈治理；天下就没有文道了。这样王道如何能兴起呢？我因此而忧虑啊。”弟子退下，先生取琴弹奏《诗经·荡》，弟子们都感动得流下了眼泪。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-17a.11" xml:lang="en" modified="2024-12-01T23:25:25.965+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="KR3a0014-en">when you discuss proper form you do not get through to the underlying principles,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-17a.12" xml:lang="en" modified="2024-12-01T23:26:40.22+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="KR3a0014-en">that is for there to be no real proper form in All Under Heaven.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-17a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-01T23:28:09.49+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="KR3a0014-en">when you discuss ***literary form you do not get through to the underlying principles,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-17a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-01T23:28:37.144+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="KR3a0014-en">that there will be no civilised culture in All Under Heaven.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-17a.13" xml:lang="en" modified="2024-12-01T23:32:31.659+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="KR3a0014-en">The way of the true King, wherefrom will it then arise? (There is no basis for it!)</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-17a.14" xml:lang="en" modified="2024-12-01T23:33:03.218+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="KR3a0014-en">That is why I looked worried.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-17a.15" xml:lang="en" modified="2024-12-01T23:34:17.643+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="KR3a0014-en">When the follower had withdrawn the Master took the lute and strummed the Tāng tune.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-17a.16" xml:lang="en" modified="2024-12-01T23:34:36.261+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="KR3a0014-en">The entourage all wetted their lapels with tears.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-17a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-01T23:35:01.266+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="KR3a0014-zh-287cbdf3">只谈虚文而不谈治理；天下就没有文道了。这样王道如何能兴起呢？我因此而忧虑啊。”弟子退下，先生取琴弹奏《诗经·荡》，弟子们都感动得流下了眼泪。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-17a.16" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-01T23:37:10.803+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="KR3a0014-en">The rest of the acolytes all wetted their lapels with tears.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-17a.14" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-01T23:58:55.923+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="KR3a0014-en">That‘s why I'm worried.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-18a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-02T00:22:30.893+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="KR3a0014-zh-287cbdf3">“或发自本心去做，或认为有利去做，或出于畏惧去做，最后成就功业是一样的，但考察他们的德性则相差很远。”</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-18a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-02T00:25:20.349+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="KR3a0014-zh-287cbdf3">最后成就功业是一样的，但考察他们的德性则相差很远。”</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-18a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-02T00:25:39.519+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="KR3a0014-zh-287cbdf3">最后成就功业是一样的，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-18a.7" xml:lang="en" modified="2024-12-02T00:27:06.039+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="KR3a0014-en">they may be the same,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-18a.8" xml:lang="en" modified="2024-12-02T00:27:51.303+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="KR3a0014-en">but when you examine their moral virtue, then they differ widely.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-18a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-02T00:30:16.108+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="KR3a0014-en">they are (maybe) the same,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-19a.2" xml:lang="en" modified="2024-12-02T00:31:32.061+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="KR3a0014-en">Jiǎ Qióng studied the Documents (Sequel) and got to the Fate of Huán Róng,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-19a.3" xml:lang="en" modified="2024-12-02T00:32:00.887+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="KR3a0014-en">and he commented:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-19a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-02T00:32:09.081+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="KR3a0014-zh-287cbdf3">贾琼学习《续书》，读到《桓荣之命》篇，感叹说：“汉光武帝和汉明帝的功业多么盛大啊！实在有上天看顾，最后能不出现揖让之事吗？”</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-19a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-02T00:34:20.204+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="KR3a0014-en">commented:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-19a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-02T00:34:25.139+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="KR3a0014-zh-287cbdf3">感叹说：“汉光武帝和汉明帝的功业多么盛大啊！实在有上天看顾，最后能不出现揖让之事吗？”</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-19a.4" xml:lang="en" modified="2024-12-02T00:35:27.494+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="KR3a0014-en">“How imposing are emperor Guāng’s and emperor Míng’s achievements.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-19a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-02T00:35:35.675+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="KR3a0014-zh-287cbdf3">“汉光武帝和汉明帝的功业多么盛大啊！实在有上天看顾，最后能不出现揖让之事吗？”</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-19a.5" xml:lang="en" modified="2024-12-02T00:37:06.725+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="KR3a0014-en">It is Heaven that was keeping an eye on him:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-19a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-02T00:38:10.319+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="KR3a0014-en">It is Heaven that was keeping an eye on him:   【實 gives contrastive  stress on the subject and does NOT mean 實在 in this context.】</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-19a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-02T00:38:18.589+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="KR3a0014-zh-287cbdf3">实在有上天看顾，最后能不出现揖让之事吗？”</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_016-17a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#dsehnal" modified="2024-12-02T00:40:35.319+09:00" resp-del="#dsehnal" src-id="KR1h0004-de-b950a924">Das volk preist sie bis jetzt. §. 1020.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-19a.6" xml:lang="en" modified="2024-12-02T00:52:10.783+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="KR3a0014-en">He was sure to end up as a paragon of polite deference!”[Something rotten here. I have not sorted this one out yet.]</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-20a.2" xml:lang="en" modified="2024-12-02T00:53:14.619+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="KR3a0014-en">Fán Shīxuān 繁師玄 (no dates, late Suí man of letters) was about to write his Record of the Northern Qí,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-20a.3" xml:lang="en" modified="2024-12-02T00:53:24.078+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="KR3a0014-en">and he told the Master about his plans.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-20a.4" xml:lang="en" modified="2024-12-02T00:54:29.355+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="KR3a0014-en">The Master said:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-20a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-02T00:57:46.314+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="KR3a0014-en">and the Master said:   </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-20a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-02T00:58:58.998+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="KR3a0014-zh-287cbdf3">先生说：“不要轻易动笔啊</seg>
                </p>
